Our staff are passionate about your holiday and will go above and beyond to make sure your time at Bali Hai Child-free Holiday Park is the best it can be. ​ The Holiday Park Managers, Nicki & Grant, look forward to welcoming you. We're proudly a dog-friendly site (caravan & camping grounds) with a huge, luxurious pool and brand-new amenities! ​ At Bali Hai Holiday Park, you're proud to offer: ​ 32 powered slab caravan & camping sites 4 powered grass caravan & camping sites 25 unpowered caravan & camping sites 3 Sea View Villas (sleeps 2 pax) 2 Sea View Bungalows (sleeps 2 pax) ​​ Having undergone a major refresh, Bali Hai Holiday Park Mission Beach is your new holiday destination. Meet our park managers, Grant & Nicki ​ G’day! We’re Grant and Nicki – passionate park managers with a love for the outdoors, travel, and creating memorable experiences for our guests. Originally from Brisbane, we’ve just returned from an amazing year looking after a beautiful park in Broome, WA. ​ Before stepping into park management, we owned and ran a successful small cabinet-making business for over 25 years. This gave us a strong foundation in customer service, attention to detail, and building genuine relationships – skills we bring with us every day in creating warm, welcoming stays for our guests. ​ Throughout the years, we’ve had the pleasure of working at a variety of campgrounds and tourist parks across Queensland, New South Wales, and most recently, Western Australia. No matter where we are, we pride ourselves on creating a friendly and well-run environment where guests feel truly welcome, relaxed, and right at home. ​ As keen road-trippers ourselves, we love nothing more than finding the perfect camping spot to unwind – so we completely understand what makes a stay truly memorable. Joining us on our journey is Maya, our playful one-year-old Staffy and the park’s official meet-and-greet expert. She’s a big fan of people and always up for a pat. She's full of personality and loves making new friends (especially the two-legged kind)!​ Everything we do is driven by our passion for creating welcoming, well-maintained spaces where you can relax, unwind, explore, and feel at home. We take pride in offering genuine hospitality that ensures your stay is smooth, enjoyable, and unforgettable. We can’t wait to welcome you and be part of your next great adventure!
